(1, 'document', 'text/html', 'Home', 'Home', 'Welcome', 'home', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Coffea Consulting is the premier global advisor for enhancing and promoting coffee quality at every\r\nstage of the production chain, from the planted seed to the brewed cup. Because the way coffee is grown, processed,\r\nhandled, and sold is just as important as how it tastes.', '<p><span>Coffea Consulting</span> is\r\nthe premier global advisor for enhancing and promoting coffee quality at every\r\nstage of the production chain &ndash; from the planted seed to the brewed cup.&nbsp; Because the way coffee is grown, processed,\r\nhandled, and sold is just as important as how it tastes, <span>Coffea Consulting</span> also\r\nworks towards establishing sustainable production systems.&nbsp; </p>\r\n<p><img src=''assets/images/Flowersandripecherries1-custom-size-266-200.JPG'' alt=''Flowers and Cherries'' style=''float:right; padding: 0 0 0 0; margin: 0 0 0 0;'' />\r\nWith a commitment to\r\ndecision making based on scientific evidence, <span>Coffea Consulting</span> will address\r\nthe needs of your coffee-related business.&nbsp; Located in Honolulu, Hawai&lsquo;i, this company is uniquely\r\nqualified to translate research on every subject of coffee science into\r\npractical, useful information for you.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<img src=''assets/images/cross_section.png'' alt=''cross section'' style=''float:right; height:116px; padding: 0 40px 0 0;'' />\r\nThrough our unique\r\narray of services, <span>Coffea Consulting</span> can help you, your friends, and your customers\r\ntaste and think about coffee in a whole new way!</p>\r\n', 0, 4, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1130304721, 1, 1262743061, 0, 0, 0, 1130304721, 1, 'Home', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(2, 'document', 'text/html', 'About', 'About Us', 'About Us', 'about-us', '', 1, 1260159951, 0, 0, 0, 'Coffea Consulting is owned and operated by Shawn Steiman.\r\nShawn holds MS and PhD degrees from the University of Hawai&lsquo;i in the\r\nfield of Tropical Plant and Soil Sciences. He has researched various aspects of coffee science, including horticulture, biochemistry, and sensory analysis.', '<div id=''subNavDiv''>\r\n	<ul class=''nav''>\r\n		<li><a id=''a'' href=''about-us.html''>About Us</a></li>\r\n		<li><a id=''m'' href=''media.html''>Selected Media Appearances 1</a></li>\r\n                <li><a id=''m2'' href=''media-2.html''>2</a></li>\r\n		<li><a id=''s'' href=''selected-literature.html''>Selected Literature 1</a></li>\r\n		<li><a id=''lit2'' href=''selected-literature-2.html''>2</a></li>\r\n		<li style=''display:none''><a id=''z'' href=''z.html''>z</a></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=''subCopy''>\r\n[!chooseSubpage!]\r\n</div>', 0, 4, 2, 1, 1, 1, 1260159969, 1, 1281886955, 0, 0, 0, 1260159969, 1, 'About Us', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(3, 'document', 'text/html', 'Services', 'Services', 'Services We Provide', 'services', '', 1, 1260159972, 0, 0, 0, 'Whether you are a farmer, roaster, retailer or someone who loves great\r\ncoffee, Coffea Consulting has the information and expertise you need. We are true coffee experts.', '<p>Whether you are a farmer, roaster, retailer or someone who loves great\r\ncoffee, we have the information and expertise you need.&nbsp; Use the links above to navigate some of the areas in which we can assist you.</p>\r\n\r\n<div id=''subNavDiv''>\r\n	<ul class=''nav''>\r\n		<li><a id=''a'' href=''agricultural.html''>Agricultural</a></li>\r\n		<li><a id=''q'' href=''quality-assessment.html''>Quality Assessment</a></li>\r\n		<li><a id=''e'' href=''educational.html''>Educational</a></li>\r\n		<li><a id=''r'' href=''research.html''>Research</a></li>\r\n		<li><a id=''p'' href=''tastings-and-cuppings.html''>Private Tastings and Cuppings</a></li>\r\n		<li><a id=''s'' href=''sourcing.html''>Sourcing</a></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=''subCopy''>\r\n[!chooseSubpage!]\r\n</div>\r\n', 0, 4, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1260159977, 1, 1262981581, 0, 0, 0, 1260159977, 1, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(4, 'document', 'text/html', 'Contact', 'Contact Us', 'Contact Us', 'contact-us', '', 1, 1260159998, 0, 0, 0, 'For a free consultation, or additional information, email Shawn Steiman at steiman@coffeaconsulting.com or call 808-223-0982.', '<p>For a free consultation, or additional information, email Shawn Steiman at <a href=''mailto:steiman@coffeaconsulting.com''>steiman@coffeaconsulting.com</a> or call +1-808-223-0982.</p>\r\n<p><center>\r\n<img src="assets/images/cross section with labels.png" alt=''Cross Section'' style=''height: 250px; padding: 0 0 0 0;'' /></center></p>', 0, 4, 3, 1, 1, 1, 1260160004, 1, 1287389122, 0, 0, 0, 1260160004, 1, 'Contact Us', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
(5, 'document', 'text/html', 'Coffee Books', 'Coffee Books', 'Coffee books written by Dr. Steiman', 'coffee-books', '', 1, 1442264820, 0, 0, 0, 'Dr. Steiman has written several books about coffee.  Each book approaches coffee differently and are worth having in any coffee library.', '<p>\r\n<img src=''assets/images/Coffee- A Comprehensive Guide to the Bean, the Beverage, and the Industry.jpg'' alt=''Signing'' style=''float:right; height:9em; padding: 0 0 0 10px;'' />\r\n<img src=''assets/images/TheHawaiiCoffeeBookfrontcover-medium.jpg'' alt=''Book'' style=''float:right; height:9em; padding: 0 0 0 10px;'' />\r\nWhile procrastinating writing his PhD dissertation in 2008, Dr. Steiman wrote his first book, <i>The Hawai&lsquo;i Coffee Book: A Gourmet''s Guide from Kona to Kaua&lsquo;i</i>.  This first book explores coffee''s journey from the farm to the brewed cup.  All the while, it uses the Hawaii coffee industry as a case study of that journey.  This is an easy to ready book filled with something for the coffee-curious to the coffee professional.</p>\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<div style="float: right; display:inline; width: 222px; border:1px black dotted; margin: 8px 35px 0 20px; padding: 0 10px 0 0;">\r\n<form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post" target="_top">\r\n<input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick">\r\n<input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="HGN75YLD2PBEE">\r\n<table>\r\n<tr><td><input type="hidden" name="on0" value="Shipping Location">Shipping Location</td></tr><tr><td><select name="os0">\r\n	<option value="THCB - USA">THCB - USA $25.00 USD</option>\r\n	<option value="THCB - International">THCB - International $33.00 USD</option>\r\n	<option value="Coffee - USA">Coffee - USA $70.00 USD</option>\r\n	<option value="Coffee - International">Coffee - International $78.00 USD</option>\r\n</select> </td></tr>\r\n</table>\r\n<input type="hidden" name="currency_code" value="USD">\r\n<input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_buynowCC_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!">\r\n<img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1">\r\n</form>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\nIn 2013, Dr. Steiman teamed up with 2 colleagues to co-edit <i>Coffee: A Comprehensive Guide to the Bean, the Beverage, and the Industry</i> and author several chapters.  Each chapter in this book delves deep into a specific coffee topic, each written by different coffee expert.  Almost encyclopedic in its reach, this book is valuable to anyone eager to immerse themselves in coffee</p>  \r\n<p>We are proud to offer signed copies of these books, shipped directly to you.  Use the PayPay button to the right to select your book of choice and destination</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 0, 4, 8, 1, 1, 1, 1260160042, 1, 1442889239, 0, 0, 0, 1260160042, 1, 'Coffee books', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
